<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 - OMEN 서버 게이트웨이</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .login-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 48px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .error {
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .message {
            background: #51cf66;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="logo">🖥️</div>
        <h1>OMEN 서버 게이트웨이</h1>

        <% if (error === 'invalid_credentials') { %>
        <div class="error">전화번호 또는 비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.</div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (message === 'login_required') { %>
        <div class="error">로그인이 필요합니다.</div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="POST" action="/login">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="user_id">전화번호</label>
                <input type="tel" id="user_id" name="user_id" placeholder="01012345678" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit">로그인</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>